<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA98">
<l>koṇṭu vaḷarkkak kuḻaviyāyt tāṉvaḷarnta</l>
<l>tuṇṭa tulakēḻu muḷḷoṭuṅkak – koṇṭu</l>
<l>kuṭamāṭik kōvalaṉāy mēviyeṉ ṉeñca</l>
<l>miṭamākak koṇṭa viṟai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking [butter] to strengthen himself he grew as a child;</l>
<l>he took [and] ate all the seven worlds so that they were compressed inside [him]</l>
<l>– the lord who, dancing on a pot/with pots(?)  as a cowherd,</l>
<l>stayed [and] took my heart as [his] place.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
